Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get crackin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:03.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's-a-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:34.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:47.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, little sister of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the beginning of your new life!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:54.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with a bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.24,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(453,241)}Under\NOne\NRoof
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:09.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to report that Yutaka's passed and say hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:18.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll probably be causing lots of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I hope we can get along well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:24.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of this as your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me start by congratulating you on passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:29.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing she passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:33.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can meet that handkerchief girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\i1}I win at life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:36.71,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,106)}Going back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.71,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,397)}The day of Yutaka's Exams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:47.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to take you to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.32,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,106)}Right after the exams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So she talked to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:57.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and even lent me her handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that I might be able to make a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.13,0:03:02.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yutaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She might've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People like her definitely pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the baseless rebuttal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:15.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:28.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:32.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to meet her on the\Nday they announce results regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return the handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.44,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(288,327)\frz23.873}You will be notified by mail of your results.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.32,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,104)}And then
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.32,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,398)}the day of orientation and uniform fitting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:47.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to return this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to deliver this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:55.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I ended troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to ever see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never intended to have this returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:06.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried I might fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:07.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:09.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're in the same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably thought I was someone's little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I came by car today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be parting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:27.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can have a great three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a relief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already became friends with such a nice person in high school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't ask what her name was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.80,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,105)}Turning back the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.80,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,399)}Present
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you ask for her name next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling sick, Yu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I got a little carsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I took some medicine though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka's got such a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:04.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's part of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.16,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz21.832\move(74,94,56,32,0,1690)}I'll rub your back—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but you need to realize what your driving's like, Cousin Yui.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.66,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz21.832\move(54,97,40,46,0,1651)}Thanks~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I get a little blargh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:16.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the only one from my old school who's going to Ryouou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll probably get sick again like today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about if I can get along with my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl so it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:33.60,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(556,30)}Sickly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:33.60,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(478,30)}Little Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:33.60,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(399,33)}Pure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.60,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,30)}Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.60,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(122,31)}Walking Pillar of Turn-ons
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...converting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:38.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If Yu-chan got together with our Miyuki-san, it'd be pretty crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Big Sister Konata's house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up awfully early when we don't have school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:01.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm about to hit the sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was gaming all nigh—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This really is a different environment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:14.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to take exams next year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:17.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been getting a bunch of phone calls from cram schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use caller ID...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you should be able to pick out those kinds of calls immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they use unlisted numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Caller ID, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:40.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my daughter's returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we talk again then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have taken up your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded like you were having a lively conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was from a telemarketer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:58.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:02.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that you could pick out those calls immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:03.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was bored and felt like having a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked over an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be your total.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whyistherealreadyanewitem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is always a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can never show mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, there was a little item I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.96,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(135,195)}Should I exchange my points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.96,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(63,238)}...Nah...but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:21.96,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(117,277)}there's other stuff I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.46,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,132)}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.46,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,176)}I'll go on the offensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent half a day thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and ended up deciding to exchange my points...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:28.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But now there's already a new item I really want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough points left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:36.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure enjoy your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:36.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't paid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you prefer smoking or non-smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're minors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so a non-smoking table please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the restroom first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:01.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:05.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the restrooms in these places...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:08.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...usually located near the smoking section?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when we're in the non-smoking section.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:20.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a nearby water source if a fire starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have buckets and hoses, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They even have hoses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Typical of a person who's never worked out in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.05,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe to cover up the stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about this stuff while we're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like the stink or restrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:41.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, in the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:44.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a number of elementary school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:48.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...have been approached from\Nbehind while on their way to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:51.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot more cases of kids being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:55.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:55.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can understand the perpetrator's way of thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:08:59.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been all over the news for consecutive days now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet he's still going up to little kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to tell him something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:16.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but don't do anything that'll get you arrested by Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:26.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's Kagami today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She went out with some friends from her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda annoyed and then it feels like something's missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten really warm lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any homework for spring break...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's really tranquil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:16.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...only people who normally work hard have the right to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hit any place weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even recognize the characters in these robot games?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since your manga and anime preferences...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:37.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...were influenced by your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:43.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have a hard time understanding what your\Nfemale friends were talking about when you were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:48.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually saw more of that kind of\Nstuff, so there wasn't any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:51.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your final answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Final answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:12.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't they just tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And his face is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking at the clock, she must have gotten the question wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The show's already over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop guessing if they got the question right\Nbased on the amount of time left when they cut to commercial?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't take the waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And they really drag it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the point of the show?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's what Tsukasa would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my cousin, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yutaka Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:50.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my friends Tsukasa and Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're the ones Big Sister's always talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she say about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:58.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I can guess from her reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already have your graduation ceremony, Yutaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:07.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember our graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a second button from anyone, Yutaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our middle school uniform was a blazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a lot more schools are like that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:31.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...does the practice of getting\Nsomething from the person you like still exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I ever did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you read blogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it looks like quite a few people are still doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:42.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You take it from someone you like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in most cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:47.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:51.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't going to get a button be\Nthe same as confessing how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:55.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better to just confess\Nand get the guy instead of a button?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideally, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:12:59.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like anyone at your old school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was often absent from school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I did go, I would soon get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made everyone feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm all small...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I look like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so everyone always teased me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had time to like anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have no problems if you aren't picky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:28.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:29.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your graduation yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:38.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't show up very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:44.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan, what class were you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:49.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You checked the absentee section first, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:56.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The differences between middle school and high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that joining a club is no longer mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that depend on the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our school's geared towards getting into college...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:07.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so there will probably be more material at a faster pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the commute takes a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you'll need some stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The decisive difference is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...class time naps have grown longer from\Ngrade school to middle school to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially during classes you're bad at!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:21.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher sounds like he's talking in a foreign language...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:27.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't end up like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:27.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my mind just starts slipping away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:32.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought your middle school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our uniform is pretty plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I thought I could wear it normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm no longer close to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you guys do with your uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave ours to some younger neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:48.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be able to give yours to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:56.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved mine for cosplay use like Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cos..?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it really gets on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:04.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our old school, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:07.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've brought it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:11.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I kind of want to go visit my grade school and middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:15.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there have been a bunch of incidents involving trespassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so people might give you funny looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll fit in just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that wasn't a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But vacations sure pass by quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you know it, it's back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:37.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring is a pain with physical exams and measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:41.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got really athletic nerves. Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which nerves are the athletic nerves?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but congratulations on graduating, Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:53.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's all go get smashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Invite your dad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:00.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:02.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.10,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:06.48,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}W-We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:06.48,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,144)\frz13.647}She means juice~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Officer, we're still minors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:07.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we can go in those places yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just stroll on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'll never catch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it all the time when I was a student!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They never caught me once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:24.17,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(348,160)\frz13.647}So you did~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.83,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We can't, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your two relatives will get us caught.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Yu-chan's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we could go to Disneyland or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:47.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm already imposing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you don't have to go so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I already went there on a school field trip a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I had a field trip like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But were you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about the minimum height for rides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in high school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:18.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was watching this school drama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:21.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I realized there are a lot of\Ndifferences between middle school and high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:26.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They stop feeding you in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You make your own lunch or eat in the cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or buy a lunch to bring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you make a box lunch every day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This could get ugly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at games!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Skilled at many forms of communication!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even cook and do other housework!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:56.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've recently learned how much pressure an older sister feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:18:00.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to work hard with those eyes on you, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cousin Yui, wild at the wheel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cousin Yui, comes home drunk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:17.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put down something random.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cousin Yui, never serious about anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it depends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so I can understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Final answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I seriously can't take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:36.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to record a line for the actual show...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I wasn't even on screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.47,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doing it again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:40.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they thinking when they make this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:45.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I stuck with this lame crap anybody could come up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.22,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Akira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.10,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The title call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.64,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Title call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The title call...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:58.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable. Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:00.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Only my voice. My voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:03.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My appearance was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't on screen either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody gives a damn about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:09.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Windy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I ask about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I ever mention you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:21.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say a word about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you bring yourself up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like me, me, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's called being overly self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make yourself scarce, Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I'm gonna end up with a dirty mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:36.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:40.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The issue here is the fact that Akira\NKogami wasn't shown in the actual show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.66,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you. What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An idol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:46.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,An idol depends on her looks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a given that I should be on screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:49.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The staff for this episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:57.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...acted in a logic-defying manner, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:06.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.31,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(115,35)}Revenge of Akira Kogami
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.31,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(169,315)}Project Full Appearance in Actual Show!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.81,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(133,30)}The world is waiting for Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:09.81,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(436,83)}Please show your support on the home page\Nand other places
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a request from Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:11.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira needs everybody's support to appear in the actual show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:14.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So send in loads of encouragement!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.56,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Loads...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Any method works!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give them a push!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:22.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that you're dying to see me appear in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.82,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other members of the cast...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't hold a candle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:33.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to a performance that features Akira's amazing talent and charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.54,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's desperate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:33.37,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's really desperate today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:38.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't wait to see such a pretty and gorgeous performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feedback...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:47.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...can make this a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.76,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:51.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So the second this show ends, start getting to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:48.43,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.47,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.18,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um, Akira-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:52.85,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,383)}This special broadcast has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop butting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on a roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you not to get in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:04.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you more about how wonderful Akira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:08.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see a lot more of my true\Ncharm during next week's actual show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:13.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:18.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get the producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.48,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:22.32,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:25.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This week's modified manuscript was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of this program?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:27.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Lucky Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It said Lucky Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.68,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.27,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:30.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts to treat me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because your last show was a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, producers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.33,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you really shouldn't be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:38.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:38.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:42.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyagi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:45.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:06.22,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived my life wishing for excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:10.01,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Who made my dream come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:17.06,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Some futures you can guess. Some you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:20.73,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's still one thing I know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:22.36,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even to the end of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.36,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:27.70,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,These looping feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:33.58,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...warp everyone in to play with imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:36.41,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,One clear, sunshiny day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.92,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...happiness greater than magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.84,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...pours down with no end in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:43.71,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:47.68,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet again tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:50.18,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll be smiling and humming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:53.39,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring together happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.98,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:58.60,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on chasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.69,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:04.19,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,We love big dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.91,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(146,462)}The End
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:13.41,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,30)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:13.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:15.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minami Iwasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:16.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yutaka Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:17.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:20.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are supposed to introduce the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.73,0:23:22.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:23.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:24.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:26.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:27.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:29.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:31.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Change So Quickly.
